<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>How This Dad Channeled His Photography Skills Into an Oprah- and Kim Kardashian-Approved Startup</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="How This Dad Channeled His Photography Skills Into an Oprah- and Kim Kardashian-Approved Startup" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160617171104-allan-shoemake.jpeg" rel="share" />

